{"tid":2413122,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Tesla值唔值","createTime":"2021-02-18T12:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T13:38:34.000Z","uid":236002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5de26a8a3435dc5806dbcf2bbd5cc9758c749a61","tid":2413122,"uid":236002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:42:11.000Z","msg":"deloitte預估全球電動車未來十年的複合年成長率將達到29%，；電動汽車的總銷量將從2020年的250萬輛，增加到2025年的1,120萬輛，2030年達到3,110萬輛。<br />\n<br />\n電動車大致可以分為電池電動車（battery electric vehicles, BEV）、插電式混合動力車（plug-in hybrid electric vehicles, PHEV）兩大類。<br />\n<br />\n細部來看，電池電動車銷量自2018年起即增加六成，占全球電動車的74%，預估到了2030年，<strong>電池電動車銷售量將達2,530萬輛</strong>，占整體電動車的81%。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克：<strong>特斯拉年產量在2030目標年達2千萬輛。</strong>，依照計算結果，特斯拉想在2030年達到2,000萬輛的產能，需要十年維持約45%的複合成長率。<br />\n<br />\nTesla主要銷售電池電動車，預計Tesla 2030市場市佔率=2000萬/2530萬=79%市佔率。即2030年每十個買電池電動車既人有8個係買Tesla。<br />\n<br />\n再計下valuation：<br />\n2030年Tesla Price to sales ratio= 0.68<br />\n2021年同行price to sales ratio平均=0.54"},{"pid":"6e8b513f2f02a623309920b2added2971f332fab","tid":2413122,"uid":160348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:44:30.000Z","msg":"Risk is different"},{"pid":"ecac4615bc6841083331ed4fe96dfa8d777388ae","tid":2413122,"uid":177561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:48:08.000Z","msg":"無可否認佢係一直發展落去, 但現時股價是否已反映未來2-3年發展成果就唔知啦"},{"pid":"b37be68368bc2fe2fa61b0bde74dc57a17c919d8","tid":2413122,"uid":291491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T12:58:11.000Z","msg":"咁autopilot,  spaceX同starlink呢？"},{"pid":"bde78595971dfe6443e747ababe50431b7e45aba","tid":2413122,"uid":358677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:09:44.000Z","msg":"唔值快d走<br />\n比我接"},{"pid":"c2481ac3b4b38582145f4b16ea2321ab70697ca4","tid":2413122,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:15:55.000Z","msg":"緊係值啦  快啲入場啦"},{"pid":"49c8dbc7aed8a4a6fc76b09fbb08d281bf2d7c8d","tid":2413122,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T13:38:34.000Z","msg":"唔值，唔好買"}]}